@startuml seq-05-change-password
title POST /auth/change-password (authenticated)

actor "User" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n+ authenticateToken" as API <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

U -> B: Change password form
B -> API: POST /auth/change-password\nAuthorization: Bearer …\n{ currentPassword, newPassword }

API -> API: rate limit + JWT auth\nload user (authUser)
API -> API: Zod validate
alt newPassword == currentPassword
  API --> B: 400 Same password not allowed
else OK
  API -> DB: findUnique user by id
  API -> API: verifyPassword(current, hash)
  alt Wrong current password
    API --> B: 401 Incorrect current password
  else OK
    API -> API: hashPassword(newPassword)
    API -> DB: user.update passwordHash,\nauthVersion++, mustChangePassword false
    API -> DB: refreshSession.updateMany revoke all for user
    API -> API: issueSessionTokens (new pair)
    API -> DB: logAuthEvent(PASSWORD_CHANGE)
    API -> API: setRefreshCookie(new refresh)
    API --> B: 200 { token, user }
  end
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/auth.ts** (~701+).
end note

@enduml
